title: Top U.S. states based on milk production 2016 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 10 different States on X-axis for 3 groups 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Out of all 3 groups, 2016 had the highest SOME LABEL in State California and 2017 had the lowest SOME LABEL in State Washington.
Among all the States, 2017 had the highest SOME LABEL 39798.0 in State California and lowest value 6526.0 in State Washington.
There is a gap of 33272.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2017 in State California and Washington.
